Mercenary Zerpmon Male Trainer 2 (Shill Punk #1311) reporting for Duty!
A collection of Punks on the XRPL. This Punk is in collaboration with Zerpmon: https://zerpmon.world/ & can be used in their game as a Zerpmon trainer!
